    <summary>Showcasing theme features and bundled shortcodes</summary>
    
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;This post demonstrates Kaonashi&#x27;s bundled shortcodes and features.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;image-with-caption&quot;&gt;Image with caption&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;



&lt;figure class=&quot;figure&quot;&gt;
  &lt;img src=&quot;https:&amp;#x2F;&amp;#x2F;placehold.co&amp;#x2F;800x400&amp;#x2F;333&amp;#x2F;e6e2d6?text=Sample+Image&quot; alt=&quot;Sample image&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot;&gt;
