&lt;h2 id=&quot;collapsible-details&quot;&gt;Collapsible details&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;details open&gt;
  &lt;summary&gt;Click to reveal&lt;&#x2F;summary&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hidden content revealed on click. Supports &lt;strong&gt;markdown&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; and code blocks:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #CDD6F4; background-color: #1E1E2E;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;json&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #9399B2;&quot;&gt;{ &amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #89B4FA;&quot;&gt;key&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #9399B2;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;:&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #A6E3A1;&quot;&gt; &amp;quot;value&amp;quot;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #9399B2;&quot;&gt; }&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;details&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;faq-shortcode&quot;&gt;FAQ shortcode&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;


&lt;details class=&quot;faq__item&quot;&gt;
  &lt;summary class=&quot;faq__question&quot;&gt;What is Zola?&lt;&#x2F;summary&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;faq__answer&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Zola is a fast static site generator written in Rust, with hot-reload, Sass compilation, and a built-in search index.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;

  &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;details&gt;



&lt;details class=&quot;faq__item&quot;&gt;
  &lt;summary class=&quot;faq__question&quot;&gt;What is Kaonashi?&lt;&#x2F;summary&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;faq__answer&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kaonashi is a minimalist Zola theme with a terminal-inspired aesthetic, dark&#x2F;light mode, and responsive card grids.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;

  &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;details&gt;

